sentence: Biden  himself  earlier  commented  that  a  deal  was  "very  close"  Meanwhile,  fighting  continues  in  Gaza,  with  the  Hamas-run  health  ministry  saying  more  than  14,000  people  have  now  been  killed  during  Israel's  campaign  -  including  more  than  5,500  children.
Medical  charity  Doctors  Without  Borders  (MSF)  says  three  doctors  have  been  killed  in  a  strike  on  the  al-Awda  hospital  in  Gaza's  north  -  including  two  of  its  own  doctors.
And  the  World  Health  Organization  (WHO)  says  one  of  its  employees  and  her  young  family  were  killed  in  a  separate  strike.
